FBIS4-54993 "dreeu089_i_94004" FBIS-EEU-94-089 Daily Report 6 May 1994 BOSNIA-HERZEGOVINA UN Loses Serbian Tank Near Sarajevo UN Loses Serbian Tank Near Sarajevo AU0605193694 Paris AFP in English 1927 GMT 6 May 94 AU0605193694 Paris AFP English BFN [Text] Sarajevo, May 6 (AFP) -- A Bosnian Serb tank disappeared from UN surveillance Friday [6 May] less than a kilometre (half a mile) from the centre of Sarajevo while travelling from the Serb stronghold of Pale to barracks at Lukavica, on the capital's outskirts, a UN military source said. The source said the tank disappeared close to Grbavica, a downtown suburb held by the Serbs, in the exclusion zone around Sarajevo in which the United Nations has banned heavy weapons.
